---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { getPath } from '../../utils/pathUtils';
---

<BaseLayout title="Work - Padmanand Warrier" currentPage="work">
    <div class="page-container">
        <h1>Work</h1>
        
        <p>
            Five decades, five technological eras. Technologies changed, organizations evolved, 
            roles shifted. What remained constant: simplifying complexity, building bridges, 
            and moving technology from potential to impact under real constraints.
        </p>

        <section class="content-categories">
            <div class="category-card">
                <h2>
                    <a href={getPath('/work/telecom')}>
                        1980s: Telecommunications Era
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Building infrastructure when bits moved over wires and innovation happened at the silicon layer.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="category-card">
                <h2>
                    <a href={getPath('/work/enterprise')}>
                        1990s: Enterprise Systems
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Connecting organizations as networks became backbones and enterprise software meant real integration.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="category-card">
                <h2>
                    <a href={getPath('/work/microsoft-platform')}>
                        2000s: Platform Evolution
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Shaping ecosystems where hardware met software and the living room became a technology frontier.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="category-card">
                <h2>
                    <a href={getPath('/work/cloud-mobile')}>
                        2010s: Cloud & Mobile Transformation
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Rebuilding at scale when the internet became infrastructure and mobile rewrote every assumption.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="category-card">
                <h2>
                    <a href={getPath('/work/sustainable-ai')}>
                        2020s: Sustainable AI
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <p>
                    Institutionalizing responsibility as AI capability outpaces governance and sustainability becomes constraint.
                </p>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</BaseLayout>
